    "1. How do you distinguish between shutil.copy() and shutil.copytree()?"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "raw",
   "id": "798e8052",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "ans: The shutil.copy() function will copy a single file, while shutil.copytree() will copy an entire folder, along with all its contents."
   ]
